    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Microwave Sparking? Stop Use, Call Today.</h2>
    <p>Real kitchen fire risk. Unplug, use a toaster oven until we arrive. $89 residential diagnostic, waived with repair. Same-day priority across LA, OC, Ventura. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href={phoneHref} class="btn-primary">☎ Call {phone}</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Book Online</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

